Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <machine> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT machine EMPTY>
 <!ATTLIST machine
      name                NMTOKEN   REQUIRED
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
